        "description": "<p><strong>Acoustic Resonance Therapy</strong><br/><br/>SONU generates resonant frequencies — calibrated to your unique facial and sinus anatomy via a smartphone facial scan and machine learning — that (a) reduce mucosal inflammation, (b) increase mucociliary clearance (the nose's natural self-cleaning system), and (c) mechanically open the nasal airway. This is drug-free, relying entirely on the physics of sound and the body's natural response to resonance.</p>"
